The [[BlasTech Industries/Legends|BlasTech]] '''EWHB-12''' was a model of [[Heavy repeating blaster/Legends|heavy repeating blaster]] that was utilized during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. The weapon could be disassembled into sections for ease of transportation and setup. The EWHB-12 had an extremely high rate of fire, while possessing average range and accuracy. The EWHB-12 would automatically fire at targets when put on a specific setting.<ref name="The Unknown">{{TCW|The Unknown}}</ref>

